            "stanza_text": "À son tic tac mélancolique,\nLa fermière écosse des pois.\n— La nuit noire comme la poix\nS'avance d'un pas diabolique."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Cependant, qu'un chat famélique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Guigne ses deux énormes poids,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "À son tic tac mélancolique,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "La fermière écosse des pois.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Cependant, qu'un chat famélique\nGuigne ses deux énormes poids,\nÀ son tic tac mélancolique,\nLa fermière écosse des pois."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Quand son tintement métallique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Vibre dans sa cage de bois,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Je frissonne un peu, mais je bois",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "L'extase douce et bucolique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "À son tic tac mélancolique.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quand son tintement métallique\nVibre dans sa cage de bois,\nJe frissonne un peu, mais je bois\nL'extase douce et bucolique\nÀ son tic tac mélancolique."
